## рџЏ—пёЏ Build Order

### Step 1 вЂ” Project Scaffold
- Init Next.js 14 with TypeScript + Tailwind in `a:\Projects\SmartBoard`
- Configure `tailwind.config.ts` with SmartBoard color palette
- Set up `tsconfig.json` paths alias (`@/`)
- Create `.env.example` and `.env.local` (user fills values)
- Add `.gitignore`

### Step 2 вЂ” Supabase Setup
- Install `@supabase/supabase-js` + `@supabase/ssr`
- Create `lib/supabase/client.ts` and `lib/supabase/server.ts`
- Create `providers/SupabaseProvider.tsx` for session context
- Configure `middleware.ts` to protect `/dashboard` route
- Wire layout with provider

### Step 3 вЂ” Auth Pages
- Build `LoginForm.tsx` and `SignupForm.tsx` with Supabase email/password auth
- Create `/login` and `/signup` pages with branded UI
- Handle redirect after login в†’ `/dashboard`
- Show loading/error states

### Step 4 вЂ” Shared Types & Utilities
- Define `Task`, `Status`, `Priority` TypeScript types in `lib/types.ts`
- Add `cn()` utility helper in `lib/utils.ts`
- Install and configure shadcn/ui components

### Step 5 вЂ” Task Data Layer
- Build `useTasks.ts` hook: fetch all tasks, create, update, delete, reorder
- All mutations use **optimistic updates** for instant UI feedback
- Implement position recalculation logic on drag-drop reorder

### Step 6 вЂ” Kanban Board UI
- `KanbanBoard.tsx`: DragDropContext wrapping three columns
- `KanbanColumn.tsx`: Droppable area, column header with count badge, top-border color
- `TaskCard.tsx`: Draggable card вЂ” title, description preview, priority badge, date
- `AddTaskInput.tsx`: Inline input shown on "+ Add Task" click
- Empty state: dashed border + helpful prompt text
- Skeleton loader shown before data arrives

### Step 7 вЂ” Task Detail Side Panel
- `TaskDetailPanel.tsx`: Sheet/drawer component (slides in from right)
- Editable: title, description (textarea), priority selector
- Delete button with confirmation
- Auto-saves on blur / explicit Save button

### Step 8 вЂ” AI Input Bar
- `AIInputBar.tsx`: Full-width bar at top of dashboard
- POST to `/api/generate` with user's prompt
- Show "AI is breaking this down..." loading state
- On response: stagger-animate tasks into To Do column via Framer Motion
- `/api/generate/route.ts`: Validate input в†’ call Claude SDK в†’ parse JSON в†’ bulk-insert tasks в†’ return tasks

### Step 9 вЂ” Analytics Bar
- `AnalyticsBar.tsx`: Derive stats from task list (no extra DB call)
- Three animated pills: Total Tasks / Completed Today / In Progress
- Values update instantly as user moves cards

### Step 10 вЂ” Polish & Final Files
- Page-level Framer Motion layout transitions
- Drag state: card rotation + drop shadow
- Responsive layout (mobile: single column scroll)
- Add `vercel.json`
- Write `README.md`
- Final audit of all colors, spacing, animations

### Step 11 вЂ” Git & Deploy
- `git init` в†’ stage all files в†’ `git commit -m "feat: SmartBoard initial build"`
- `vercel --prod` (user runs with their env vars set in Vercel dashboard)

