## вљ™пёЏ Environment Variables

```bash
# .env.example
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The user must create a Supabase project, run the SQL schema above in the Supabase SQL editor, and paste their keys into `.env.local` before starting the dev server.

